{"tid":2395034,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"曾經被欺凌過嘅你依家過成點？","createTime":"2021-02-04T15:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T14:49:49.000Z","uid":325757,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"0de1d719359ee15b4261c5e28590481e4f20970e","tid":2395034,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:20:52.000Z","msg":"借朋友ac<br />\n<br />\n終於轉到新環境唔洗延續痛苦，但係嗰種創傷跟到依家 你地如果曾經被欺凌，到最後係點走出陰霾，定還是每隔一段時間都會因為咁唔開心，係咪無可能再好返<br />\n<br />\n會唔會過左某個歲數就唔會再受煎熬，真係唔想再受呢種痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e2d6fc07c11235f953701b905ee91dc9d7e69b","tid":2395034,"uid":208323,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:21:40.000Z","msg":"日日俾人欺凌都過得唔錯"},{"pid":"da1b945bfdcbbaf52b104da9f08f7d236e1940db","tid":2395034,"uid":69221,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ut5GkKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUt5GkKu.png&h=134fbff5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3dead59cd10890e518878c5f396bb8ea03302bf","tid":2395034,"uid":54930,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:24:51.000Z","msg":"中學欺凌我果條友之前上電視，我咪乘機係連登狙擊佢，想佢身敗名裂，點知呢度d人唔撐我，仲話返我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b7fb133e98f2ac883fb90c99bac618ad4eec74","tid":2395034,"uid":249170,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"成功置業，準備結婚"},{"pid":"c0f24117c83e4e8ee4c01d17977c8218381ce0f1","tid":2395034,"uid":229642,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:27:39.000Z","msg":"依家過得好好，可以盡情發掘自己興趣，唔洗驚畀人笑。過往嘅事一直會時不時諗起，我永遠唔會忘記曾經令我陷入情緒苦難中嘅人，我亦唔會輕易原諒、唔會輕易放底。"},{"pid":"68aeba203af9726be97bd75d66fe6dcd70906b24","tid":2395034,"uid":78243,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:29:23.000